quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  23,18,"Uye tinodzikisa mvura kubva kudenga nesimba (redu), toiita kuti ive nenzvimbo yekugara pano pasi, uye zvirokwazvo, tine simba rekuitora (mvura)"
  23,19,"Uye tinokukudzirai nayo mapindu emadheti nemagirepu, muine michero mizhinji yenyu, iyo yamunodya"
  23,20,"Uye muti (weOrivhi) unomera mugomo reSinai, unoburitsa mafuta, uye muriwo kune avo vanodya"
  23,21,"Uye zvirokwazvo kubva mumhuka (mombe) mune chidzidzo kwamuri. Tinokupai kuti munwe izvo zviri mumatumbu adzo (mukaka). Uye madziri mune zvizhinji zvinokubatsirai, uye kubva kwadziri munodya"
  23,22,Uye pamusoro padzo (mhuka) uye ngarava munova munotakurwa (munzendo dzamunofamba)
  23,23,"Uye zvirokwazvo takave tinotuma Nowa kuvanhu vake, akave anotaura kuti: “Imi vanhu vangu! Namatai Allah! Hamuna vamwe mwari kusara kwavo. Saka hamuve munovatya here?”"
  23,24,"Asi madzimambo asingatendi pakati pevanhu vake vakataura kuti: “Uyu murume (munhu) akafananawo nemi, uye ari kuda kuva pamusoro penyu. Uye dai Allah vaida (kutumira mutumwa), zvirokwazvo vaitumira ngirozi. Hatisati tambonzwa zvakadai kubva kumadzibaba edu (madzitateguru edu).”"
  23,25,"“Uyu murume ari kupenga, saka chimbomirai maererano nezvake kwekanguva kadiki.”"
  23,26,"Nowa akati: “Tenzi vangu! Ivai munonditsigira nekuti vave vanondiramba.”"
  23,27,"Saka takave tinotaura (tinotumira) kwaari (kuti): “Vaka ngarava uri pasi pemeso edu uye nemashoko edu. Uye kana mutsigo wedu wauya, uye mvura yatanga kubuda kubva muchitofu, isa mungarava kubva kuchisikwa chimwe nechimwe zviviri zviviri (chirume nechikadzi), uye nemhuri yako, kusara kweavo kubva kwavari vakave vanotarwa kuti vachave vanoparadzwa. Uye usave unotaura neni maererano neavo vakave vanotadza. Zvirokwazvo, vari kuva vanonyudzwa.”"